            <h1 class="font-1 fw-bold text-white">Palliative Care</h1>
            <h4 style="color:white;">Comfort focused care that prioritises dignity, peace, and quality of life.</h4>

            <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                <ol class="breadcrumb">
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item fw-bold"><a asp-page="/Index">Home</a></li>
